text: Ærest of ðære cyricean norðeast hyrnan nygan girda andlang stræte <uton> ða cypinge.
Swa up anlang cypinge eahta gyrda ðet hit cymh to Wistanes gemære.
Swa andlang Wistenes gemere nygon girda ðæt hit cymh on ðone wæterpyt.
Fram ðam wæterpyt X <gyrda> andlang strete to ðære cyrcean norðeast hyrnan.
